data.description: Nestled in the heart of Sulphur, this precious cottage is more than a home—it's an invitation to a lifestyle where comfort, style, and a vibrant community seamlessly come together. Located in a charming, walkable neighborhood, the allure of gorgeous hardwoods welcomes you as you ascend the steps, setting the stage for a residence that beautifully blends character with contemporary updates.  The layout unfolds with a wonderful flow, featuring two bedrooms in the front, sharing a hall bathroom. A master bedroom, a secluded retreat at the rear of the home, basks in natural light pouring through many windows, creating a serene and inviting atmosphere.  The heart of the home boasts a natural gas-powered range oven and water heater, catering to culinary enthusiasts and efficiency seekers alike. The convenience extends to the laundry room, providing easy access to the fenced backyard—ideal for enjoying outdoor moments in privacy.  Freshly painted interiors breathe new life into the space, creating a canvas for your personal touch. Safety is a priority with the property being wired for an ADT alarm system, offering peace of mind for you and your loved ones.   Beyond the cottage's boundaries, discover a walkable neighborhood with proximity to schools, The Grove, and downtown—a hub for both convenience and community.  Whether you're seeking a great starter home or an investment property, this cottage is ready to welcome you. It's not just a residence; it's your new haven in the heart of Sulphur. Welcome home!
